<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Financial PR - Quarterly Results</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background: #fff;
            color: #000;
            line-height: 1.5;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        
        .press-release {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .press-release > font[size="5"] {
            display: block;
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        
        .press-release p {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: justify;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-indent: 0;
        }
        
        .press-release blockquote {
            margin: 24px 0;
            padding: 16px;
            border-left: 4px solid #003366;
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }
        
        .press-release blockquote font[size="2"] {
            display: block;
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #003366;
        }
        
        .press-release blockquote table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }
        
        .press-release blockquote table td {
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .press-release blockquote table td:first-child {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .press-release blockquote table td:last-child {
            text-align: right;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        
        .press-release font[size="3"] font[color="#000080"] {
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .press-release > font[size="2"] {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .disclaimer {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: left;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .press-release > font[size="3"]:last-of-type {
            display: block;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-left: 3px solid #003366;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="press-release">
        <font size="5" color="#003366"><b>Cascading Industries Reports Strong Q4 2024 Financial Results</b></font>
        
        <p><font size="3">NEW YORK - Cascading Industries (NYSE: CID) today announced financial results for the fourth quarter ended December 31, 2024, showing significant growth across all business segments with revenue increasing by 18% year-over-year and operating margins expanding to 24.3%.</font></p>
        
        <p><font size="3">The company's performance was driven by strong demand for its enterprise solutions portfolio, particularly in the cloud computing and artificial intelligence sectors where Cascading Industries has made substantial strategic investments over the past eighteen months.</font></p>
        
        <blockquote>
            <font size="2">Financial Summary (in millions USD):</font>
            <table border="1">
                <tr>
                    <td>Revenue</td>
                    <td>$4,230</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Operating Income</td>
                    <td>$1,028</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Net Income</td>
                    <td>$787</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>EPS</td>
                    <td>$3.42</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </blockquote>
        
        <p><font size="3">"We are pleased with our execution this quarter," said <font color="#000080"><i>CEO Margaret Chen</i></font>. "Our team has delivered outstanding results while simultaneously investing in next-generation technologies that will drive long-term growth."</font></p>
        
        <p><font size="3">Looking ahead to 2025, the company expects continued momentum with revenue guidance of $4.8 to $5.1 billion, reflecting confidence in its product pipeline and market position.</font></p>
        
        <font size="2" color="#666666">About Cascading Industries: Leading provider of enterprise software solutions serving Fortune 500 clients worldwide.</font>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
